latestIgtvVideos.title: Gifting New Phone To Dad (Dec 2019)
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Last year, I decided to gift papa his favourite Iphone.
He was using Iphone 6 back then.. but you all know the life of smartphones.. and papa being papa is never ready to spend on himself (though he always bought every latest gadget for me) .. so you knowww

This video is really special to me.. gifting something to your parents that once they gifted to you is a special feeling.. (that to from your hard-earned money 🙈).. That particular moment was, is & will always be really special to me.. so I thought of sharing it with you all

PS: I shot this vlog last year i.e. 2019
But because the video and sound quality wasn't really good, so, I didn't upload it on YouTube.

PPS: I LOVE YOU PAPA ❤
.
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Nighttime Skincare Routine For Summers
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So, my nighttime skincare routine goes like this
1) I remove all my makeup using @garnierindia miceller water
2) I cleanse my face using @himalaya_facecare purifying neem face wash
3) To tone I use Dabur Rose Water
4) To keep my skin hydrated and moisturizer I apply @plumgoodness gree tea night gel

To know more about my CTM routine, go to my YouTube channel 'TakenByHue' or just click on the link mentioned in my bio
Thank you ❤
